summary: This is a calendar entry for an FBI-organized briefing for Epstein victims, scheduled for October 2, 2019, in a New York conference room. It lists FBI and other government agency attendees and includes a note correcting the start time.

events.title: Epstein Victim Briefing
events.description: A briefing organized by the FBI for victims of Jeffrey Epstein, scheduled to take place in a conference room in New York.

keyFacts: The FBI scheduled a briefing for Epstein victims on October 2, 2019.
The event was to be held at the 290 9th Floor Conference Room in New York.
Attendees included personnel from the FBI's New York and Domestic Operations offices, as well as other government agencies (OGA).
A note in the calendar corrects the start time from 1:30 PM to 1:00 PM.
The document is a calendar entry, indicating official planning and coordination for victim outreach by law enforcement.
